#tbt Almost five years ago to the day, I finished my very first commercial design project. I worked for FREE in exchange for full creative license. 400 sq ft. 4 chairs. 1 bath. 
This was, and still is, one of my proudest moments as a designer. I was scared half to death…my first custom millwork design (the stations and dividers), my first time managing an outside contractor…sheesh! I did that! And I will forever owe @amourjah for giving me a chance to show the world what I have to offer. 
Every so often, look back and smell the roses peeps. This was a 10x moment (iykyk). I needed this reminder today…that I can do ALL things because God’s got me, that I am completely and utterly in my purpose right now, and even the toughest of days are making me better. 
In short: big up yourself!!! 💪🏾💪🏾

#tbt #nw10interiors #salondesign #saloninteriors #braidsalon #custommillwork #smallspaces
